data.description: Well kept home with 2 large bedrooms and 2 baths is ready for a new owner. It has two living rooms, a cozy fireplace and a bonus room off the living room. The Yard is spacious in front and behind the house and has plenty of parking for cars, RV, or any toys you might have.  The whole property is gated and the house is located above the street to enjoy a view of the neighborhood and surrounding mountains.  Do not hesitate to schedule a private tour today.
